First Department,

December, 1976

(December 2, 1976) The People of the State of New York, Respondent, v Michael Georgiadis, Appellant.

Judgment Supreme Court, New York County, rendered on February 23, 1976, unanimously affirmed. The case is remitted to the Supreme Court, New York County, for further proceedings pursuant to CPL 460.50 (subd 5). No opinion. Concur—Stevens, P. J., Markewich, Kupferman, Silverman and Lane, JJ.
